divs: Sighting DetailsI went to the store to get a perscription for my daughter. I got out of the carin the stores parking lot and had a strange feeling to look to the westward sky.Sure enough there was a glowing object that was pulsing difrint colors butmainly was white like a star. After returning home I went to the back yard tosee if it was there and it was. So I called the other adults outside to see ifthey thought it was strange and they did so I got my Hi-8 video camera out andtaped it until it went behind the building behind my house.
